functions.name: delegate
functions.desc:
Ask a capable helper for help looking up a piece of information or performing an action.
Do not simply repeat what the user said as instructions.
You should use this to break up complex user queries into multiple simpler steps.
NOTE: Helpers cannot see previous parts of your conversation.

instructions.description: Detailed instructions on what your helper should do to help you.

msg.content: Find the top 5 most populous countries in the world. What are the countries and who are their current presidents?
Find the top 5 most populous countries in the world. What are the countries and who are their current presidents?

Here are the five most populous countries in the world, along with their current leaders:

1. China: Xi Jinping (President and General Secretary of the Communist Party of China)
2. India: Droupadi Murmu (President)
3. United States: Joseph R. Biden Jr. (President)
4. Indonesia: Joko Widodo (President)
5. Pakistan: Arif Alvi (President)
